            </li>
            <li class="list-main__item">
                layout - settings of layout, heading and footer
            </li>
            <li class="list-main__item">
                libs - third parties components
            </li>
            <li class="list-main__item">
                helpers - helpers, that have to be loaded last
            </li>
            <li class="list-main__item">
                components - components of content part, subfolders divide components logically apart
                <ul class="list-main">
                    <li class="list-main__item">
                        IN - small components (arrow by link, evaluation asterisks) small things that occur often on more places
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-main__item">
